{"tid":1062354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★60後猝斃麥當勞廁格！","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T09:48:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d93a2533b8af4749cbcd59407acdfb4fe7af2011","tid":1062354,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】中年漢快餐店如廁猝死！現場紅磡必嘉街卅七至卅九號麥當勞快餐店，昨晨七時許，有顧客進入店內男廁時，發覺廁格門反鎖，拍門良久無人回應，遂通知職員協助。姓陳（四十七歲）男職員查看，赫然發現一名男子在廁格內暈倒，由於身體擋門未能開啟，遂報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方及消防員趕至將廁格門打開，救護員經檢驗後，發現該名男子已死亡，屍體僵硬。其後，證實死者姓李（五十二歲），警員翻查店內閉路電視片段，發覺李在案發前兩小時已進入廁所。警方聯絡李父到場協助，獲知李生前有患病紀錄，不排除他因病暈倒失救致死，事件無可疑，惟死因待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190315/00176_062.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2F00176_062.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsad6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ad61b788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190315/00176_062.html</a>"},{"pid":"efca3b86fa18d4102ec1310a4c0be7e1ccae5994","tid":1062354,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"work die?"},{"pid":"98ee39b4b4e9a7dd3e06da81af4cd4194de8ddfb","tid":1062354,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:52:35.000Z","msg":"陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ab90eca5297b9fd462dc69e6f38d0e3e0c3736","tid":1062354,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efca3b86fa18d4102ec1310a4c0be7e1ccae5994","tid":1062354,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"work die?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"似"},{"pid":"8ff679c01175029adee090ba47da551f3003b8e8","tid":1062354,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"朱